s=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌你老母"},{"pid":"9fa4786cec4b2fbf06c3030f449168821bdf96e4","tid":1846503,"uid":20368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"幾百萬湖北人係其他省蠢蠢欲動<br />\n黎香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5726cd75afb977fa5089667be9a42c8bc9ecfb","tid":1846503,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dde7a7b9210ab4fd1f95d1b54e05d9b77437c679","tid":1846503,"uid":259267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"係湖北居民 應該係因為身份證寫咗咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"身分證唔係既而又中咗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2daaa6e84a8e52dd9f826fcae8af64a4bf9b94eb","tid":1846503,"uid":140596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"大家請幫手轉告，我地一定要向政府施壓<br />\n時間已經唔多。一日就係一日，我地唔可以畀沙士再現一次 ，所有醫護一個都不能少<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>-必需延長新年法定假期</strong>， 由最短至2月2日為原則，隨時延長至另行通知。減少員工於工作環境交叉感染機會。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>-任何內地回來香港的必需自行隔離14日，期間不得上班，</strong>， 需向政府申報地址顧主不得借此理由裁減員工，可向政府報銷一半工資。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>-短期內封閉內地關口</strong>，所有內地自由行入境之旅行必須在指定時間內向政府匯報位置及進入隔離營等候遣返，如沒有症狀的將會遣返原地。限期後將會採用即捕即解及列入永久黑名單計劃。在內地需回港居民將即接先送去隔離營作檢查，等待檢測結果才能回家。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>-醫療用品將於各民政事務署可作以市價發售給持香港有效身分證居民購買</strong>，有關用品會有記錄不得倒賣。如有經濟問題的市民則由社署處理醫療物資派發。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>-任何隔離政策選扯以減輕居民影響為原則</strong>， 需定於離島或解放軍未使用之設施，香港居民及疫區人士分開安置。"},{"pid":"fa345ee9fe87a5a4014df6783ccb43296686324c","tid":1846503,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:15:35.000Z","msg":"見一個內地人就趕一個內地人走！<br />\n唔係就送佢哋入警署！<br />\n到香港人保家衛族嘅時候啦！"},{"pid":"091e0d3483d29e51cc5ce5c127ae66b2ef71b01e","tid":1846503,"uid":267864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:19:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一階段，最簡單、最可行的封關要求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最簡單的做法： 只容許港人、公務、商務及探親簽註進入。其實簡單來說就是暫時取消自由行及旅行團，回覆03年前的內地對自由行的出入境管制及不容許旅行團進入。是可以在5分鐘內宣佈並24小時內執行的。香港的入境處絕對有能力做到過濾。<br />\n<br />\n當然可能還會有不少人能進入，但是必然少很多很多倍！<br />\n後續的封關可以再做，但這個必須立刻做！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/visas/overseas-chinese-entry-arrangement.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservices%2Fvisas%2Foverseas-chinese-entry-arrangement.html&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5mWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=58ee9432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/visas/overseas-chinese-entry-arrangement.html</a>"},{"pid":"01cdb2b2af6ce5232cba69623432a59f202092c5","tid":1846503,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"澳門趕走晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbaf3cfe9b9c850c3d0498d755de89de28709749","tid":1846503,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:21:42.000Z","msg":"張身份證好誠實"},{"pid":"5ca9a975173e6ddcea64d61851feff6319c784c7","tid":1846503,"uid":284630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9f155ae5c6f8e5caa694f9c89ffb9eae310067d5","tid":1846503,"uid":19552,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"02e5e4ad42c3e9e2f702cfb8475115b5426a7f6e","tid":1846503,"uid":30476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"邊單新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"今日一共拒絕394個報稱去過湖北既人入境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:23:50.000Z","msg"